|-
| {{lang|ko-Hang-KP|할가요}}
| halgayo (halkayo)
| {{lang|ko-Hang-KR|할까요}}
| halkkayo (halkkayo)
| Shall we do?
| Although the hangul differ, the pronunciations are the same (i.e. with the tensed ㄲ sound).
|}

